OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,FPrecautionary antibiotics and
OL,8,FMeningitis B vaccinations will be
OL,9,Foffered to more than 6,500 young
OL,10,Fpeople in parts of Dorset following
OL,11,Fthree confirmed cases in the county.
OL,13,FThe three people have now been
OL,14,Fdischarged from hospital and there are
OL,15,Fno further suspected or confirmed
OL,16,Fcases to date.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
