OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,FMore than 1800 pupils at Budmouth
OL,8,FAcademy and Wey Valley Academy were
OL,9,Fgiven antibiotics, out of a total of
OL,10,F2500 students offered them at these
OL,11,Fschools, on 19 April.
OL,13,FNow, students in years 7-13 across
OL,14,FWeymouth, Portland and Chickerell will
OL,15,Fbe offered the medication.
OL,17,FAnyone eligible but not in full-time
OL,18,Feducation in those locations can
OL,19,Faccess antibiotics from Tuesday
OL,20,Fafternoon at All Saints Academy until
OL,21,FFriday 24 April.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,FPupils attending Atlantic Academy,
OL,8,FKingston Maurward Academy and
OL,9,FCoastland Academy will also be invited
OL,10,Ffor antibiotics and vaccination this
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
