OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,FDr Beth Smout, UKHSA Deputy Director,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are really pleased to see
OL,9,Fsuch high uptake of the antibiotic
OL,10,Foffer over the weekend. Antibiotics
OL,11,Fare the best course of action if there
OL,12,Fis a chance you have been exposed to
OL,13,Fmeningococcal bacteria, with MenB
OL,14,Fvaccination offering longer term
OL,15,Fprotection against becoming seriously
OL,16,Fill.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,F"Thanks to the swift action from
OL,8,FDorset Council, local partners and NHS
OL,9,Fstaff, over 6500 young people in the
OL,10,Farea will be able to access
OL,11,Fantibiotics, with vaccination to
OL,12,Ffollow in the coming weeks.
OL,14,F"Thankfully we have seen no further
OL,15,Fcases of meningitis, but it's still
OL,16,Fimportant to recognise the signs and
OL,17,Fsymptoms.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,F"Symptoms can include a fever,
OL,8,Fheadache, rapid breathing, drowsiness,
OL,9,Fshivering, vomiting and cold hands and
OL,10,Ffeet.
OL,12,F"Septicaemia can also cause a
OL,13,Fcharacteristic rash that does not fade
OL,14,Fwhen pressed against a glass. If the
OL,15,Fdisease is suspected, you should seek
OL,16,Fimmediate medical attention as the
OL,17,Fdisease can progress rapidly."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
