OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,FDawn Dawson, Chief Nursing Officer of
OL,8,FDorset HealthCare and Dorset County
OL,9,FHospital, said: "I'd like to thank all
OL,10,Fof the families, NHS colleagues and
OL,11,Fall partners who have worked so hard
OL,12,Fto help us to deliver the antibiotics
OL,13,Fto the children and young people of
OL,14,FWeymouth at such speed over the
OL,15,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
