OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776764340
OL,3,CAntibiotics and Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccination offered more than 6,000
OL,5,Cyoung people
OL,7,F"It has been an amazing multi-agency
OL,8,Fresponse, and we continue to work
OL,9,Ftogether to make sure that antibiotics
OL,10,Fand vaccinations reach the remainder
OL,11,Fof the children and young people in
OL,12,Fthe eligible population this week."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
